Hi, I'm Maxime!

I'm a self-taught full stack developer with over a decade of experience. I've built web applications of all sorts, and also created free browser extensions that are used daily by hundreds of thousands users \o/.

A little More About Me...

I'm a passionate coder. My top skills are HTML, CSS, JavaScript (which is my preferred programming language), PHP, Python. I'm also comfortable with SQL and NoSQL databases, as well as web servers (Node.js and NGINX). This site doesn't reflect my skills and needs to be updated, but I'm too busy for that... so if you are looking for a full stack developer, keep searching ^^, because I only work for local companies now and because maintaining my browser extensions and providing support is comparable to a full time job!

href="https://www.namecheap.com/support/knowledgebase/article.aspx/1055/?utm_nooverride=1&utm_source=privateemail.com&utm_medium=landing_page&utm_campaign=try_it_for_free">by using this guide</a></p> </div> </article> <i id="steps-trigger2"></i> <article class="steps__item" id="step3"> <span class="steps__num">3</span> <div class="steps__image"><img src="/appsuite/login-assets/images/1220b72adc1455523e6ea79f36a55e3f.svg" alt="Step 2" width="480"></div> <div class="steps__dsc"> <h3 class="steps__title">Connect your device</h3> <p>You can access Private Email via Webmail, or configure your mail client to retrieve and send messages through IMAP, POP3 or SMTP. <a target="_blank" href="https://www.namecheap.com/support/knowledgebase/article.aspx/1179/?utm_nooverride=1&utm_source=privateemail.com&utm_medium=landing_page&utm_campaign=try_it_for_free">Click here</a> to find the settings for desktop and mobile clients.</p> </div> </article> </div> <div class="faq"> <h2 class="faq__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2> <h3 class="faq__subtitle">Browse through the frequently asked questions</h3> <div class="open-close"> <div class="open-close__row"> <h3 class="open-close__opener">What is email hosting?</h3> <div class="open-close__slide"> <div class="open-close__content"> <p>Email hosting is a service in which a hosting provider rents out email servers to its users. While some companies offer basic free hosting options, you get more from premium services that offer more flexibility and power. Professional web-based email hosting takes place when both incoming and outgoing emails are managed by a separate shared or dedicated mail server.</p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="open-close__row"> <h3 class="open-close__opener">How do I set up a business email?</h3> <div class="open-close__slide"> <div class="open-close__content"> <p>Professional or business email creation may seem complicated, but actually, it is not as scary as it looks. Once your desired business email domain is chosen and the email hosting is purchased, all that's left to do is <a target="_blank" href="https://www.namecheap.com/support/knowledgebase/article.aspx/1338/2176/namecheap-private-email-dns-records-for-domains-on-namecheap-basicpremium-nameservers/">set up your DNS records</a>. After that, you will be able to <a target="_blank" href="https://www.namecheap.com/support/knowledgebase/article.aspx/1049/2215/how-to-create-namecheap-private-email-mailbox/">create a mailbox</a> and enjoy the email service.</p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="open-close__row"> <h3 class="open-close__opener">Why choose Namecheap Private Email?</h3> <div class="open-close__slide"> <div class="open-close__content"> <p> Namecheap Private Email is a collaborative, open-source software. It provides a fresh, modern design that works across tablets, desktops, and laptops – allowing users to communicate whenever and wherever they want. Create public spaces in shared folders, set and control tasks, create and manage work schedules, and much more with our bespoke email platform. </p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="open-close__row"> <h3 class="open-close__opener">How do you transfer emails to your Namecheap Private Email account?</h3> <div class="open-close__slide"> <div class="open-close__content"> <p> If you are using a third-party email service and would like to switch to our Private Email, you can easily migrate your old emails (Inbox, Sent and other folders) to our servers using the Webmail interface. In order to transfer old emails to your email hosting account, follow <a target="_blank" href="https://www.namecheap.com/support/knowledgebase/article.aspx/9566/2226/how-to-transfer-emails-to-namecheap-private-email-account/?utm_nooverride=1&utm_source=privateemail.com&utm_medium=landing_page&utm_campaign=try_it_for_free">these steps</a>. </p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="open-close__row"> <h3 class="open-close__opener">Can I use a personal email domain with Namecheap Private Email?</h3> <div class="open-close__slide"> <div class="open-close__content"> <p>Whether you want to have a personal email or a business email, Namecheap Private Email allows you to create a custom email address with the domain name of your choice.</p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="open-close__row"> <h3 class="open-close__opener">Email etiquette</h3> <div class="open-close__slide"> <div class="open-close__content"> <p> Looking for tips on best email practices for businesses? Professionals all communicate with a certain degree of formality in language. Respond with courtesy, pleasantries and directness and you’ll be on your way to a <a target="_blank" href="https://www.namecheap.com/hosting/email-etiquette/?utm_nooverride=1&utm_source=privateemail.com&utm_medium=landing_page&utm_campaign=try_it_for_free">beneficial business relationship</a>. </p>
